<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.7.4">
<l>māṟu cērpaṭai nūṟṟuvar maṅka vōraivark kāyaṉṟu māyappōr paṇṇi</l>
<l>nīṟu ceyta ventāy nilaṅkīṇṭa vammāṉē</l>
<l>tēṟu ñāṉattar vēta vēḷviyaṟāc</l>
<l>cirīvara maṅkalanaka rēṟivīṟ ṟiruntā yuṉṉai yeṅkeytak kūvuvaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O my father who, so that the Hundred with a hostile army were diminuished, waged magical war</l>
<l>that days for the sake of the unique Five [and] laid [the foes] into ashes, lord who split the ground,</l>
<l>you who rose [and] sit in distinction in the city of Cirīvaramaṅkalam where the Vedic sacrifices of the one</l>
<l>with clear knowledge do not cease, I call out in order to reach you where?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
